# LiveKit Plugins Llama Index

Agent Framework plugin for using Llama Index. Currently supports [Query Engine](mdc:https:/docs.llamaindex.ai/en/stable/module_guides/deploying/query_engine) and [Chat Engine](mdc:https:/docs.llamaindex.ai/en/stable/module_guides/deploying/chat_engines).

## Install

```bash
pip install livekit-plugins-llama-index
```


full example [here](mdc:https:/github.com/livekit/agents/blob/main/examples/voice-pipeline-agent/llamaindex-rag/chat_engine.py)
